text: Loránd Milassin (18 January 1948 – 1 April 2021) was a Hungarian hurdler. He competed in the men's 110 metres hurdles at the 1972 Summer Olympics. Milassin was born in Budapest. Milassin died on 1 April 2021 in Budapest, aged 73.Elhunyt Milassin Lóránd ==References== Category:1948 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Olympians for Hungary Category:Hungarian athletes Category:Hurdlers Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
